<h3>Question 8</h3>
<div><p><p>You are working as the manager of an IT company. Write an email encouraging your staff to work for some additional hours every week so that the company and staff equally benefit.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>FROM:</strong> ram74@gmail.com</p>
<p><strong>TO:</strong> employee1@gmail.com</p>
<p><strong>SUBJECT:</strong> On working additional hours every week.</p>
<p><strong>Dear Staffs,</strong></p>
<p>This email is being sent to inform you about the increase in the number of working hours for all the employees in effect from July 12, 2023. We know that this project has been taking a taking huge time. As the deadline is near for our project, I request you all to work some additional hours every week. Our company will benefit a lot if we put in some effort. The work should equally benefit its all hardworking and dedicated staff. So, we should take responsibility for our laziness but things are about to change. I truly ensure that we can make this happen through our extreme willpower and continue to raise our name and fame in the coming days. Hope this email encourages you.</p>
<p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>
<p><strong>Yours Truly</strong><br />
Program Coordinator</p>
</div>
